jokes.text: I went to buy some camo pants but couldn’t find any.
I always find elevator jokes to be uplifting.
Most people are shocked when they find out how bad I am as an electrician.
I’ve had a perfectly wonderful evening, but this wasn’t it.
I failed math so many times at school, I can’t even count
Did you hear about the man who was afraid of negative integers? He'd stop at nothing to avoid them.
What did the nut saying while chasing another nut? I'm a cashew!
I'm afraid for the calendar. Its days are numbered.
What do a tick and the Eiffel Tower have in common? They're both Paris sites.
I thought the dryer was shrinking my clothes. Turns out it was the refrigerator all along.
